  "title": "IT Communications Manager",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Manage internal and external IT-related communications</p></li><li><p>Coordinate between IT teams and business users</p></li><li><p>Prepare IT announcements, updates, and reports</p></li><li><p>Support IT projects with clear communication plans</p></li><li><p>Ensure consistent messaging across systems and platforms</p></li></ul><h3>Job Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in IT or Communications, or Any field with more than 5 years experience </p></li><li><p>Basic understanding of IT systems and digital platforms</p></li><li><p>Good written and verbal communication skills</p></li><li><p>Ability to coordinate with multiple teams</p></li><li><p>Organized, detail-oriented, and able to meet deadlines</p></li></ul>",
